<!--**********************************************************************
    *                                                                    *
    *                        S1000D Issue 2                              *
    *                SGML Document Type Definition                       *
    *                                                                    *
    *                     Release Version 2.2                            *
    *                       Date: 2005-05-01                             *
    *                                                                    *
    * Amendment:-                                                        *
    * 1. Update public identifier date.                                  *
    * 2. CPF 2004-32US: Moved paracon entity out of COMMON.ENT into      *
    *                   static and interactive declaration files.        *
    *                                                                    *
    * Typical invocation:-                                               *
    * <!ENTITY % PARACONINTERACT PUBLIC                                  *
    *   "-//S1000D//ENTITIES Paracon Interact Breakdown 20050501//EN" >  *
    * %PARACONINTERACT;                                                  *
    ********************************************************************** -->


<!--**********************************************************************
    * Define Entity %paracon; (Paragraph Continuation) containing:-      *
    *====================================================================*
    * Mandatory Repeatable Group.                                        *
    *====================================================================*
    *  Definition stored in entity %text;.                               *
    * or                                                                 *
    *  Definition stored in entity %list;                                *
    *  Definition stored in entity %CAPPCON;                             *
    * or                                                                 *
    *  variable-ref - Mandatory  Single      contains No Other Tags.     *
    *====================================================================*
    ********************************************************************** -->

<!ENTITY % paracon "(%text; | %list; %CAPPCON; | variable-ref)+" >
